summary: A RaceMenu Preset of Venturian's character Vahl
descriptionHtml:
I downloaded the Vahl follower mod and was able to get the facegen from the mod to use as a preset. This character comes from the youtube channel [url=http://www.youtube.com/user/venturiantale]VenturianTale[/url]. I had to configure it a little but that is besides the point.

Mods Required:
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/66568/?]A Skyrim Tale Follower - Vahl The Dragonborn Dimension Walker[/url] by MCab719
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35267/?]SG Female Textures Renewal[/url] by hellosanta
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?]The Eyes of Beauty[/url] by Gabriel Mailhot
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/2666/?]CBBE[/url] by Caliente (Adult Content) or [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/6709/?]DIMONIZED UNP Female Body[/url] by dimon99 (Adult Content) 
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/24273/?]Ethereal Elven Overhaul[/url] by Nuska
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/30411/?]Brows[/url] by Hvergelmir
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/31797/?]Ponytail Hairstyles[/url] by Azar
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]RaceMenu[/url] by expired6978

Installation:
1. Install Mods Above
2. Unzip File
3. place in Steam\SteamApps\common\Skyrim\Data\SKSE\Plugins\CharGen\Presets
4. Open Game
5. Click the Presets Tab and Click f9
6. Name Character and Have Fun!!!

Know Issues:
Will load default hair. Just pick the hairstyle in the photos using the sliders.

Special Thanks
MCab719 for making this possible.
author: Syvalion
